# Session start

Before substantive work in this repo, read:

1. `notes/agents/README.md` — agent folder rules and current status
2. `notes/agents/cursor-plans/INDEX.md` — active plans and current truth

If `notes/` is empty, seed from `docs/vault-starter/agents/` (see `docs/obsidian-vault.md`).

## Current truth (update INDEX when this changes)

- App version: see `package.json` and `build-info.json`
- Local DB: SQLite WAL at `data/cabinet_pm_tablet.db`
- Sync: HTTP sync-server → MongoDB; legacy direct-Mongo fallback if `SYNC_API_URL` unset
- Tablet build: `npm run build` → `dist/CabinetPM.exe`
- Git: `main` = releases; `develop` = active work
